						               													<description>When it comes to food, lots of people are willing to do anything. And with that bustling market in that food business, you wouldn't miss a chance to pick up the opportunity for your food joint rise up into fame and fortune. That's not all, popularity race is on the take and you need to snatch one of them to boost its fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Assign your workers to fetch ingredients to different place in the neighborhood and take orders from your customers. Serve Indonesian authentic food dishes and get various kind of rewards. With calculated planning and right opportunities, your joint might be the next big thing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Nusa Rasa is a simple worker placement game with resource management, area majority and set collection, that pits players in a competitive business of restaurants serving local authentic dishes from across Indonesia provinces. The game offers 2 distinct modes (family and advance), in which have similar game play but different feel and approach.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Family Mode&amp;#10;Simple worker placement game where players assign workers to get resources they need to serve order cards and get rewards. Players can serve orders any time during their turn without limitation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Advance Mode&amp;#10;Unlike Family mode, now in Advance more, there are Serving Phase  occurs after each three rounds of the game. Players may only serve orders in this phase and there is penalty if they cannot serve the orders that they had. They also need to pay their workers and resources are discarded after they serve orders. This mode provides experienced players more challenge and planning to consider. The game is designed to be harder than the normal Family mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
